00:10:11.790 --> 00:10:16.590
talk about three policy
changes of varying significance

00:10:16.590 --> 00:10:20.190
that have happened in the last
30 years in the United States.

00:10:20.190 --> 00:10:26.930
The first is the passage
of the 1981 budget proposal

00:10:26.930 --> 00:10:30.740
by President Ronald Reagan,
which dramatically reduced taxes.

00:10:30.740 --> 00:10:34.290
The second is the closure of
