00:12:56.220 --> 00:12:59.360
Which slow things down, but
they're not exactly a filibuster.

00:12:59.360 --> 00:13:02.430
So I started thinking, why would
a minority be doing these things,

00:13:02.430 --> 00:13:05.290
just to cause a little bit
of difficulty I suppose.

00:13:05.290 --> 00:13:09.810
And the other was in 2008
I was fortunate enough

