00:13:55.270 --> 00:13:57.950
There are categories of
activities that they do.

00:13:57.950 --> 00:13:59.470
The second is why.

00:13:59.470 --> 00:14:01.820
Why do they do the
things that they do?

00:14:01.820 --> 00:14:06.220
The third is have the things that
the minority party, does the things

00:14:06.220 --> 00:14:08.650
that they do, has it
changed over time?

00:14:08.650 --> 00:14:14.260
And the fourth is whether it has
any effects on politics or policy.

